description: Rumblee is the main protagonist of the Tales of Madao Hazard, the game added to the "original" Gintama game, revised by http://anidb.net/ch7827 [Tama] with http://anidb.net/ch1162 [Gintoki]`s guidance. In game, Rumblee came to Edo, looking for http://anidb.net/ch93102 [her brother] who became a zombie NEET.
name: Ranbubiyo
